package kz.fearsom.financiallifev2.i18n.translations

// Generated from ruStrings to cover game content keys that previously fell back to Russian.
internal val enContentStrings: Map<String, String> = mapOf(
    "evt_era_ussr_collapse_msg" to "December 1991. The USSR collapsed.\n\nBanks froze deposits. Hyperinflation - money becomes worthless\nevery week. Half of the enterprises stopped.\n\nEverything that was in the savings bank burned down.",
    "evt_era_ussr_collapse_opt_barter_survive" to "Switch to natural exchange - food is more important than money",
    "evt_era_ussr_collapse_opt_hard_currency" to "Urgently convert balances into dollars",
    "evt_era_tenge_introduced_msg" to "November 1993. Kazakhstan introduced its own currency - the tenge.\n\nSoviet rubles are exchanged at a rate of 500:1.\nThere are queues at the exchangers, people are panicking and tired.\n\nYou have cash rubles - what are you doing?",
    "evt_era_tenge_introduced_opt_exchange_all" to "Exchange everything immediately - while there is a limit",
    "evt_era_tenge_introduced_opt_wait_see" to "Wait - maybe the rate will improve",
    "evt_era_mmm_wave_90s_msg" to "1994. MMM is advertised throughout the CIS - Sergey Mavrodi promises 1000% per month.\nTV, newspapers - Lenya Golubkov is everywhere.\n“I’m not a freeloader, I’m a partner!”\n\nThe neighbor invested his entire salary and has already “earned” 3 times more.\nThey offer you to invest too.",
    "evt_era_mmm_wave_90s_opt_invest_mmm" to "Invest - everyone around you makes money",
    "evt_era_mmm_wave_90s_opt_skeptical" to "Giving up is too good to be true",
    "evt_era_mmm_collapse_msg" to "MMM collapsed. Mavrodi was arrested.\nThe shares are worth zero. The money has disappeared.\n\nTens of millions of people lost their savings.\nYou are one of them.\n\nThis was the main lesson of the 90s: “there is no such thing as free cheese.”",
    "evt_era_mmm_collapse_opt_accept_lesson" to "Accept the lesson. No more pyramids.",
    "evt_era_mmm_skeptic_result_msg" to "MMM collapsed after 4 months. Millions have lost everything.\n\nYour neighbor is shocked - he invested everything he had.\nYou saved the money because you didn't give in to the hype.\n\nCaution cost you lost profits, but saved your capital.",
    "evt_era_mmm_skeptic_result_opt_be_grateful" to "It's good that I didn't invest. I'll remember this lesson.",
    "evt_era_devaluation_2015_msg" to "August 20, 2015. The National Bank announced the transition to a free exchange rate for the tenge.\n\nIn one day, the dollar rose from 188 to 256 tenge.\nThe tenge fell by 36%.\n\nYour savings are in tenge. They just lost a third of their real value.",
    "evt_era_devaluation_2015_opt_convert_to_dollar" to "Buy dollars urgently - before it's too late",
    "evt_era_devaluation_2015_opt_keep_tenge" to "Keep it in tenge - maybe it will win back",
    "evt_era_devaluation_2015_opt_buy_property" to "Buy something real - an apartment or equipment",
    "evt_era_covid_shock_2020_msg" to "March 2020. Pandemic. Complete lockdown.\n\nCompanies are laying off en masse. Restaurants, shops - everything is closed.\nTenge fell again. Exchanges collapsed by 30-40%.\n\nThose who had an airbag survived it calmly.\nDo you have a pillow?",
    "evt_era_covid_shock_2020_opt_has_cushion_good" to "There is a pillow - we will survive calmly",
    "evt_era_covid_shock_2020_opt_no_cushion_crisis" to "There is no pillow - I’m urgently looking for any job",
    "evt_era_covid_shock_2020_opt_buy_dip" to "The market has fallen - I buy ETFs on the drawdown",
    "evt_era_covid_recovery_gain_msg" to "A year has passed. The markets recovered from the fall and grew.\n\nThe ETF bought at the bottom in March 2020 is now worth 1.7 times more.\n+70% for the year is the best result over the last decade.\n\nThe crisis became an opportunity for those who did not panic.",
    "evt_era_covid_recovery_gain_opt_celebrate_wisdom" to "Excellent result. I'll keep it going.",
    "evt_era_kz_devaluation_2022_msg" to "March 2022. War in Ukraine. Sanctions against Russia.\nThe tenge fell by 20% in a week.\n\nEverything imported has risen sharply in price.\nThe dollar is now 470 tenge.\n\nWhat do you do with your savings?",
    "evt_era_kz_devaluation_2022_opt_diversify_currency" to "Split: 50% in dollars, 50% in tenge for expenses",
    "evt_era_kz_devaluation_2022_opt_panic_buy_dollar" to "Buy all dollars at any rate",
    "evt_era_kz_devaluation_2022_opt_ignore_it" to "Do nothing - it will sort itself out",
    "scam_pyramid_neighbor_90s_msg" to "The neighbor on the staircase called for tea.\n\n“Listen, there is a reliable way. You invest 50,000, a month later - 100,000.\nI already received it. The neighbor from the third one too. There are documents. The company is official.\"\n\nHe takes out a beautiful brochure with a profitability table.",
    "scam_pyramid_neighbor_90s_opt_invest_full" to "Invest 50,000 - your neighbor won’t deceive you",
    "scam_pyramid_neighbor_90s_opt_ask_docs" to "Ask for documents - look carefully",
    "scam_pyramid_neighbor_90s_opt_small_bet" to "Invest 10,000 - “I’ll try on a small amount”",
    "scam_pyramid_neighbor_90s_opt_decline" to "Refuse - “thank you, not mine”",
    "scam_pyramid_email_2005_msg" to "An email arrived - the address was given by someone I knew.\n\n“Dear, I invite you to the financial club. Contribution 100,000 ₸,\nguaranteed income of 40% per month. We have been working officially since 2003.\nCall to make an appointment.\"\n\nThen Bauyrzhan himself called - he says he’s been in the system for six months already,\neverything is transparent, no risk. Offers to meet in a cafe.",
    "scam_pyramid_email_2005_opt_invest_full" to "Invest 100,000 ₸ — Bauyrzhan has known me for a long time",
    "scam_pyramid_email_2005_opt_ask_docs" to "Request official company documents",
    "scam_pyramid_email_2005_opt_small_bet" to "Invest 20,000 ₸ - “I’ll try”",
    "scam_pyramid_email_2005_opt_decline" to "Refuse - “busy, I’ll call you back later” (and not call back)",
    "scam_pyramid_vk_2015_msg" to "Asan wrote on VKontakte: “Come in, there’s a topic.”\n\n“Listen, I found something. I have already received 80,000 ₸ for the month.\nMom also contributed. 100% guarantee. You need at least 100,000 ₸.\nSend me a WhatsApp and I’ll explain the scheme, everything is legal there.”\n\nAsan is an old friend. But something in the voice sounds too... salesy.",
    "scam_pyramid_vk_2015_opt_invest_full" to "Invest 100,000 ₸ - Asan is a childhood friend",
    "scam_pyramid_vk_2015_opt_ask_docs" to "Ask for documents - how exactly is money earned?",
    "scam_pyramid_vk_2015_opt_small_bet" to "Invest 20,000 ₸ - “I don’t mind losing”",
    "scam_pyramid_vk_2015_opt_decline" to "Refuse - “not my topic, sorry”",
    "scam_pyramid_friend_msg" to "Asan called late in the evening, his voice was excited.\n\n“Listen, I found something. I have already received 80,000 ₸ for the month.\nMom also contributed. 100% guarantee. You need at least 100,000 ₸.\nI’m responsible for you, do you trust me?”\n\nAsan is an old friend. But something in the voice sounds too... salesy.",
    "scam_pyramid_friend_opt_invest_full" to "Invest 100,000 ₸ - Asan is a childhood friend",
    "scam_pyramid_friend_opt_ask_docs" to "Ask for documents - how exactly is money earned?",
    "scam_pyramid_friend_opt_small_bet" to "Invest 20,000 ₸ - “I don’t mind losing, it’s interesting to try”",
    "scam_pyramid_friend_opt_decline" to "Refuse - “not my topic, sorry”",
    "scam_pyramid_avoided_msg" to "Couldn't explain where the income comes from.\n“Well... there’s a system, smart people do it...”\n\nGoogled it - a classic financial pyramid.\nThe first participants actually receive money - from new investors.\nMathematics inevitably leads to collapse.\n\nAfter 3 months I received a message: “You were right. Everything collapsed.\"",
    "scam_pyramid_avoided_opt_lesson_learned" to "It's good that I figured it out. I will remember the signs of a pyramid.",
    "scam_pyramid_collapse_msg" to "The pyramid collapsed. The phone is not available.\n100,000 tenge are lost forever.\n\nThe organizers disappeared. The police are investigating, but there is no chance.\nReal investment does not require attracting new people.",
    "scam_pyramid_collapse_opt_rebuild" to "Accept the loss. Never again.",
    "scam_pyramid_small_loss_msg" to "At first 8,000 ₸ arrived - everything seemed real.\nThen - silence. Payments have stopped.\n\nLost 12,000 ₸ net. A small amount, but an important lesson.",
    "scam_pyramid_small_loss_opt_lesson" to "Got off cheap. Now I know the signs of the pyramids.",
    "scam_mlm_door_90s_msg" to "The doorbell rang. Unfamiliar woman with a large bag.\n\n\"Hello! I represent Herbalife.\nThese products will change your life! And you can earn money yourself -\nyou just need to buy a starter kit for 50,000 ₸ and invite your friends.”\n\nShe showed a magazine with success stories. Everyone is happy, everyone is thin.",
    "scam_mlm_door_90s_opt_go_meeting" to "Buy a set - “I’ll try to sell to neighbors”",
    "scam_mlm_door_90s_opt_ask_directly" to "Ask: “How much do they really earn?”",
    "scam_mlm_door_90s_opt_decline" to "Politely close the door",
    "scam_mlm_phone_2005_msg" to "An acquaintance called - no see for a long time.\n\n“Listen, I’m in an interesting business now. Cosmetics, vitamins.\nI have already earned 80,000 ₸ in 2 months. Let's meet on Saturday\nI'll introduce you to the team. Just watch.\"\n\nThere were about 15 people at the meeting, beautiful booklets, stories of success.\nAt the end: “Starter set - 35,000 ₸. Registration today.\"",
    "scam_mlm_phone_2005_opt_go_meeting" to "Buy a set - “I’ll try for a month”",
    "scam_mlm_phone_2005_opt_ask_directly" to "Ask directly: “How much do most people actually earn?”",
    "scam_mlm_phone_2005_opt_decline" to "Refuse - “I’ll think about it”",
    "scam_mlm_instagram_2015_msg" to "Colleague Aigul has changed - she’s lost weight, has new things, is happy.\nShe posted a photo with the training on Instagram: “I’m now an entrepreneur!”\n\n“Come to the meeting on Friday - just take a look.\nI’ll add you to our WhatsApp chat, there’s a video with the results.”\n\nShe used to complain about her salary. I wonder what happened.",
    "scam_mlm_instagram_2015_opt_go_meeting" to "Go and “just have a look”",
    "scam_mlm_instagram_2015_opt_ask_directly" to "Ask directly: “Is this an MLM?”",
    "scam_mlm_instagram_2015_opt_decline" to "Politely refuse - busy",
    "scam_mlm_colleague_msg" to "Colleague Aigul has changed recently - she’s glowing, has new clothes.\nShe says: “I found amazing products! And now I'm an entrepreneur.\nCome to the meeting on Friday - just look, don’t sign anything.”\n\nShe used to complain about her salary. Now I’m happy. I wonder what happened.",
    "scam_mlm_colleague_opt_go_meeting" to "Go and “just have a look”",
    "scam_mlm_colleague_opt_ask_directly" to "Ask directly: “Is this an MLM?”",
    "scam_mlm_colleague_opt_decline" to "Politely refuse - busy",
    "scam_mlm_presentation_msg" to "Meeting in a cafe. Beautiful slides, success stories.\n“Invite two - they will invite two - passive income in a year!”\n\nAt the end: “Starter set of products - 35,000 ₸. Only today with a discount.”\nThey look with hope. You are important to them as a “partner”.",
    "scam_mlm_presentation_opt_join" to "Buy a starter kit - “I’ll try for a month”",
    "scam_mlm_presentation_opt_decline_after" to "Refusing after a presentation is “not my thing”",
    "scam_mlm_confronted_msg" to "95% of MLM distributors do not recoup their initial investment - this is a fact from FTC research.\n\nA real business is built on selling a product, not on recruiting.\nIf the main income from attracting new people is a pyramid with a product.\n\nPerhaps they will be offended. But you saved money and time.",
    "scam_mlm_confronted_opt_understand" to "Understood. Thanks for the lesson.",
    "scam_mlm_month_later_msg" to "3 months in MLM. The reality is:\n\nSold products worth 8,000 ₸.\nSpent on “mandatory purchases”: 105,000 ₸ (3 months × 35,000).\nThe warehouse at home is filled with unsold goods.\n\nWe need to purchase 35,000 again to maintain the “rank of director.”\nContinue or quit?",
    "scam_mlm_month_later_opt_exit" to "Exit - losses are recorded, it will get worse further",
    "scam_mlm_month_later_opt_continue" to "Continue - “one more month and everything will go”",
    "scam_capper_sms_2005_msg" to "I received an SMS from an unknown number:\n“I give 3 free sports forecasts. 1st: CSKA will win today.”\n\nCSKA won 2:0. Then the second prediction is also correct.\nThen the call: “See the accuracy? Paid package - 15,000 ₸ per month.\nI work with bookmakers directly.”",
    "scam_capper_sms_2005_opt_buy" to "Pay 15,000 ₸ - three out of three are correct!",
    "scam_capper_sms_2005_opt_research" to "Search on the Internet about the “forecast fork scheme”",
    "scam_capper_sms_2005_opt_ignore" to "Delete SMS - too suspicious",
    "scam_capper_vk_2015_msg" to "VKontakte received a personal message from a stranger:\n“I’ll give you 3 free forecasts. Make sure it's level.\nFirst: Barcelona will win today.\"\n\nBarcelona won. The second forecast came true. The third one too.\n\n“Do you see the level? Paid access for a month - 25,000 ₸.\nI haven’t started a Telegram channel yet, I work directly.”",
    "scam_capper_vk_2015_opt_buy" to "Buy access for 25,000 ₸ - three out of three are correct!",
    "scam_capper_vk_2015_opt_research" to "Google “capper forecast arb scheme”",
    "scam_capper_vk_2015_opt_ignore" to "Block - too suspicious",
    "scam_capper_telegram_msg" to "An unfamiliar account wrote on Telegram: “I’ll give you 3 free forecasts.”\n\nFirst: Real Madrid will beat Barca. Won 2:1 - that's right.\nThe second one agreed. The third one too. Three out of three is impressive.\n\n“Do you see the level? Paid access for a month - 30,000 ₸.\nThe first month I return the money if you don’t earn money.”\n\nInteresting. But how does a stranger know my number?",
    "scam_capper_telegram_opt_buy" to "Buy access for 30,000 ₸ - three out of three are correct!",
    "scam_capper_telegram_opt_research" to "Google “capper forecast arb scheme”",
    "scam_capper_telegram_opt_ignore" to "Block - too suspicious",
    "scam_capper_explained_msg" to "The scheme is called a “forecast fork”:\n\n1000 people → 500 get “A will win”, 500 get “B will win”.\n500 were right → 500 unsubscribed.\nAfter 5 rounds - 30 people with a “magic” series of 5/5.\nThey are sold paid access.\n\nThis is pure mathematics, not analytics.",
    "scam_capper_explained_opt_lesson" to "I understood the mechanics. I don't buy this.",
    "scam_capper_loses_msg" to "The forecasts began to fail. 3 out of 5 - negative.\n\nCapper explains: “A losing streak, the market is unpredictable.\nBuy an annual package - there are closed matches with a guarantee.”\n\nMoney lost. Additionally, they offer to invest another 100,000.",
    "scam_capper_loses_opt_stop" to "Stay. This is a diagram, not an analysis.",
    "scam_capper_loses_opt_escalate" to "Buy an “annual package” - win back losses",
    "scam_betting_deep_loss_msg" to "Capper has disappeared. The channel has been deleted. The number is blocked.\n\nChasing losses is a trap.\nThe more you lose, the stronger the desire to “win back.”\nThis is called gambling addiction.",
    "scam_betting_deep_loss_opt_final_lesson" to "Expensive. Never - bet on the money you need.",
    "scam_romance_mamba_2015_msg" to "A stranger wrote on VKontakte and said, “I found it through mutual friends.”\n\nNice profile. She says she works in Almaty, moved from Shymkent.\nSmart, understands jokes. He writes every day for two weeks.\n\nToday I mentioned it for the first time: “My uncle taught me to trade Forex.\nDo you want me to show you? I have already earned 200,000 ₸ in a month.”",
    "scam_romance_mamba_2015_opt_respond" to "Reply - interesting about Forex",
    "scam_romance_mamba_2015_opt_suspicious" to "Check profile - account created a month ago",
    "scam_romance_mamba_2015_opt_ignore" to "Don't answer - stranger",
    "scam_romance_contact_msg" to "Today I received a strange message on WhatsApp from an unfamiliar number.\n“Hi, I think I got the wrong number 😊 Do you know the Arai cafe on Dostyk?”\n\nBeautiful profile, photos from different countries. He says he works as a consultant in Dubai.\nI’ve already written three times - she’s interested, asks questions, and is very attentive.\n\nProbably just a lonely person. Or not?",
    "scam_romance_contact_opt_respond" to "Reply - I wonder who it is",
    "scam_romance_contact_opt_suspicious" to "Check your number and profile for fraud",
    "scam_romance_contact_opt_ignore" to "Do not answer - unknown number",
    "scam_romance_buildup_msg" to "2 months of communication. He understands like no one else.\nSmart, beautiful in the photo, talks interestingly about money.\n\n“My uncle taught me how to make money on the platform.\nI’m not suggesting it - just look at the screenshot of my account.”\n\nOn the screen - 4,800,000 ₸. “That’s how it works if you know where to look.”",
    "scam_romance_buildup_opt_interested" to "“Tell me more” - it’s interesting to try",
    "scam_romance_buildup_opt_red_flag" to "Wait - does your friend immediately move on to money?",
    "scam_romance_crypto_intro_msg" to "Helped me register on the “platform”.\nI invested 50,000 ₸ - in the interface they grew to 74,000 ₸ in a week!\n\n“See? Can be withdrawn at any time. But it's better to hold -\nin a month it will be 150,000.” Offers to invest more.",
    "scam_romance_crypto_intro_opt_more_money" to "Invest another 200,000 ₸ - the numbers really grow!",
    "scam_romance_crypto_intro_opt_withdraw_test" to "Try to withdraw - check that the money is real",
    "scam_romance_withdrawal_blocked_msg" to "When I tried to withdraw, the following message appeared:\n“To verify the account, you must pay a tax of 15% - 7,500 ₸.”\n\nAfter payment - new: “For withdrawals of more than 50,000, international verification is required - 50,000 ₸.”\n\nExplains: “These are temporary, mandatory platform procedures.”",
    "scam_romance_withdrawal_blocked_opt_pay_tax" to "Pay “tax” - the money is visible in the interface",
    "scam_romance_withdrawal_blocked_opt_realize" to "Waiting is a classic sign of scam",
    "scam_romance_freeze_msg" to "“The account has been frozen by regulatory checks. Temporarily.\nTo defrost, you need to top up up to 500,000 ₸ - this is a requirement of the platform.”\n\nAlready 250,000 ₸ within the system. It is impossible to withdraw.\nHe continues to write - affectionately, with explanations.",
    "scam_romance_freeze_opt_pay_more" to "Top up another 250,000 - otherwise I’ll lose everything invested",
    "scam_romance_freeze_opt_stop_loss" to "Stay. 250,000 is a loss. Don't add.",
    "scam_romance_final_msg" to "Profile has been deleted. Platform unavailable. The number is blocked.\n\nEverything that was entered disappeared. This is \"Pig Butchering\":\nfirst they are “fed” with trust, then they are “cut”.\n\nFraudsters work from organized centers, they have scripts and training.",
    "scam_romance_final_opt_report" to "Report to the police. Learn how the circuit works.",
    "scam_romance_caught_msg" to "I checked the profile in the scam databases - there are complaints.\nPhotos taken from stock. The number is not picking up.\n\n“Romantic scam” scheme: 2-3 months build trust,\nthen they introduce an “investment platform”.\n\nCaution saved you.",
    "scam_romance_caught_opt_safe" to "Good thing I checked. I will be more attentive to strangers online.",
    "scam_crypto_forex_2015_msg" to "I read about Bitcoin on the forum - they say it has grown 10 times in a year.\nA stranger wrote in a personal message: “I’ll help you get into Forex - there’s legal income there.”\n\n“Register on the platform, deposit 100,000 ₸.\nAutomatic trading, income 5% per week. Conclusion whenever.\"\n\nThe platform looks serious - graphics, analytics, English interface.",
    "scam_crypto_forex_2015_opt_crypto_exchange_invest" to "Register and deposit 100,000 ₸",
    "scam_crypto_forex_2015_opt_crypto_exchange_check" to "Check the license in the financial regulator register",
    "scam_crypto_forex_2015_opt_crypto_exchange_ignore" to "Ignore - unlicensed platforms are dangerous",
    "scam_crypto_exchange_msg" to "Subscribed to a Telegram channel with 52,000 subscribers - the analyst gives “signals”.\nThe first 3 turned out to be correct. Now recommends a new exchange:\n\n“Register, import USDT - auto trading gives 8% per week.\nWithdrawal at any time. Minimum 50,000 ₸. Checked personally.\"\n\n52 thousand people are reading - it can’t all be a hoax?",
    "scam_crypto_exchange_opt_crypto_exchange_invest" to "Register and deposit 100,000 ₸",
    "scam_crypto_exchange_opt_crypto_exchange_check" to "Check the exchange license in the National Bank register",
    "scam_crypto_exchange_opt_crypto_exchange_ignore" to "Ignore - unlicensed exchanges are dangerous",
    "scam_crypto_no_license_msg" to "This platform is not included in the register of the National Bank of the Republic of Kazakhstan.\nOn the Internet there are forums with reviews that “do not allow you to withdraw money.”\n\nSubscribers to the channel can be purchased for 5,000 rubles.\nThree correct predictions - “fork pattern”, simple mathematics.\n\nLegal sites operate with real licenses.",
    "scam_crypto_no_license_opt_crypto_lesson" to "Understood. Checking the license is a mandatory step.",
    "scam_crypto_withdrawal_trap_msg" to "The balance in the interface has increased - it looks great.\nWhen trying to withdraw: “Pay the verification fee - 15,000 ₸.”\n\nAfter payment: “The account is marked as suspicious.\nA deposit of ₸200,000 is required to confirm identity.”",
    "scam_crypto_withdrawal_trap_opt_crypto_pay_more" to "Pay 15,000 - maybe they will unblock",
    "scam_crypto_withdrawal_trap_opt_crypto_stop_now" to "Stay. This is a classic trap.",
    "scam_crypto_final_disappear_msg" to "The site has disappeared. The channel is blocked.\n\nScheme - “fake exchange”:\nbeautiful interface with growing numbers, but real money goes to scammers.\nWhen withdrawing, “taxes” and “verifications” appear endlessly.\n\nThe regulator's license is the first thing to check.",
    "scam_crypto_final_disappear_opt_crypto_final_lesson" to "A bitter lesson. Now I know how to check.",
    "scam_mfo_neighbor_90s_msg" to "The refrigerator is broken. I need 50,000 ₸ urgently, but banks won’t give it without collateral.\n\nMy friend Rustem says: “I’ll give you 10% a month. Without papers, like a neighbor.\nIn a month you will return 55,000 - and that’s it, no problems.”\n\n10% per month is 120% per annum. But money is needed today.",
    "scam_mfo_neighbor_90s_opt_mfo_take_quick" to "Borrow from Rustem - quickly and conveniently",
    "scam_mfo_neighbor_90s_opt_mfo_read_contract" to "Calculate: 10% per month = 120% per year. That's a lot.",
    "scam_mfo_neighbor_90s_opt_mfo_call_bank" to "Try to borrow from relatives",
    "scam_mfo_office_2005_msg" to "The refrigerator is broken. I need 80,000 ₸ urgently.\nThe bank is considering the week. On the street I see a sign: “Microcredit - 15 minutes.”\n\nI'm coming in. The manager smiles: “No certificate, no collateral.\n0% first month! Then 3% per day.”\n\n3% per day = 1000% per annum. But it's written small.",
    "scam_mfo_office_2005_opt_mfo_take_quick" to "Apply to a microfinance organization - quickly and conveniently",
    "scam_mfo_office_2005_opt_mfo_read_contract" to "Read the entire contract before signing",
    "scam_mfo_office_2005_opt_mfo_call_bank" to "Wait for the bank - MFOs are too expensive",
    "scam_mfo_urgent_msg" to "The refrigerator is broken. All contents are missing - 80,000 ₸ is needed urgently.\n\nThe bank says 3-5 days for review. MFO online - approval in 15 minutes.\nThe website says: “0% for the first 30 days!” - sounds good.\nAt the very bottom in small print: “after 30 days - 2% per day.”\n\nI'm not in the mood for fine print right now. Or is it worth reading?",
    "scam_mfo_urgent_opt_mfo_take_quick" to "Apply to a microfinance organization - quickly and conveniently",
    "scam_mfo_urgent_opt_mfo_read_contract" to "Read the entire contract before signing",
    "scam_mfo_urgent_opt_mfo_call_bank" to "Call the bank - ask for urgent consideration",
    "scam_mfo_urgent_2024_msg" to "The refrigerator is broken. All contents are missing - 80,000 ₸ is needed urgently.\n\nThe bank says 3-5 days for review. MFO online - approval in 15 minutes.\nThe website says: “0% for the first 30 days!” - sounds good.\nAt the very bottom in small print: “after 30 days - 2% per day.”\n\nI'm not in the mood for fine print right now. Or is it worth reading?",
    "scam_mfo_urgent_2024_opt_mfo_take_quick" to "Apply to a microfinance organization - quickly and conveniently",
    "scam_mfo_urgent_2024_opt_mfo_read_contract" to "Read the entire contract before signing",
    "scam_mfo_urgent_2024_opt_mfo_call_bank" to "Call the bank - ask for urgent consideration",
    "scam_mfo_contract_revealed_msg" to "I read the contract. Here's what's really there:\n\n• Rate: 2% per day = 730% per annum (this is legal!)\n• Late fee: 0.5% of the amount per day additionally\n• After the “free” period: the debt grows like a snowball\n\nExample: took 80,000 → did not return on time → after 3 months the debt is 200,000+.\n\nMFO - only for extreme cases with guaranteed quick return.",
    "scam_mfo_contract_revealed_opt_mfo_understand" to "Understood. It’s better to wait for the bank or borrow from relatives.",
    "scam_mfo_signed_msg" to "Took the money. I solved the problem.\n\nAfter a month there is no required amount to return.\nThe rate moves to 2% per day.\nA month later, the debt had already increased by one and a half times.\n\nMFO calls every day. Stress is growing.",
    "scam_mfo_signed_opt_mfo_pay_urgently" to "Urgently borrow from relatives and pay off the debt",
    "scam_mfo_signed_opt_mfo_rollover" to "Get another one from another microfinance organization to close this one",
    "scam_middleman_turkey_90s_msg" to "Neighbor Rustem returns from Turkey once a quarter with goods.\n“Listen, let’s chip in - I’ll bring clothes and equipment.\n4 times cheaper than in the store. You need 200,000 ₸.\nIn 2 months I will bring goods worth 400,000.”\n\nNo papers. “Why an agreement between neighbors?”\nRustem really travels - here is his photo from Istanbul.",
    "scam_middleman_turkey_90s_opt_middleman_invest" to "Invest 200,000 ₸ - a good margin!",
    "scam_middleman_turkey_90s_opt_middleman_ask_contract" to "Only with a receipt - I don’t work without papers",
    "scam_middleman_turkey_90s_opt_middleman_decline" to "Refuse - too cloudy without documents",
    "scam_middleman_alibaba_2005_msg" to "A friend says: “I found the Alibaba website - there are goods from factories in China.\nLet's chip in, I'll arrange delivery. 500,000 ₸ —\nin 2 months you will receive goods worth 800,000. My margin is 10%.”\n\nNo contract. “Why an agreement, we’re acquaintances?”\nAlibaba is a real site - it's not a scam, is it?",
    "scam_middleman_alibaba_2005_opt_middleman_invest" to "Invest 500,000 ₸ - a good margin!",
    "scam_middleman_alibaba_2005_opt_middleman_ask_contract" to "Only with a contract - I don’t work without papers",
    "scam_middleman_alibaba_2005_opt_middleman_decline" to "Refuse - too cloudy without documents",
    "scam_middleman_ali_2015_msg" to "An acquaintance, Kanat, wrote on WhatsApp:\n“I buy directly from AliExpress factories - 3 times cheaper than the store.\nInvest 500,000 ₸ - in 2 months you will receive goods worth 800,000. My margin is 10%.”\n\nI asked about the contract. “Why an agreement, we’re acquaintances? Offended.\"\nHm. We are acquaintances - but not that close.",
    "scam_middleman_ali_2015_opt_middleman_invest" to "Invest 500,000 ₸ - a good margin!",
    "scam_middleman_ali_2015_opt_middleman_ask_contract" to "Only with a contract - I don’t work without papers",
    "scam_middleman_ali_2015_opt_middleman_decline" to "Refuse - too cloudy without documents",
    "scam_middleman_china_msg" to "An acquaintance, Kanat, wrote with a proposal for “partnership.”\n\n“I buy goods directly from Chinese factories - 3 times cheaper than the store.\nInvest 500,000 ₸ - in 2 months you will receive goods worth 800,000. My margin is 10%.”\n\nI asked about the contract. “Why an agreement, we’re acquaintances? Offended.\"\nHm. We are acquaintances - but not that close.",
    "scam_middleman_china_opt_middleman_invest" to "Invest 500,000 ₸ - a good margin!",
    "scam_middleman_china_opt_middleman_ask_contract" to "Only with a contract - I don’t work without papers",
    "scam_middleman_china_opt_middleman_decline" to "Refuse - too cloudy without documents",
    "scam_middleman_contract_refused_msg" to "“Why an agreement between friends? Don’t you trust me?”\n\nPressure through trust is a classic sign of fraud.\nAny legal transaction has documentary evidence.\n\nIf a person refuses an agreement, he is hiding something important.",
    "scam_middleman_contract_refused_opt_middleman_lesson" to "I did the right thing. The contract protects both parties.",
    "scam_middleman_result_msg" to "2 months have passed. The goods did not arrive.\nAt first he answered: “Delay at customs.”\nThen: “Force majeure, we need another 100,000 for additional money. expenses\".\nNow he doesn't pick up the phone.\n\nMoney lost. There is no agreement - the court will not help.",
    "scam_middleman_result_opt_middleman_loss_lesson" to "Money lost. Lesson: any deal is only with an agreement.",
    "scam_training_kiyosaki_90s_msg" to "On the street they gave a leaflet: “Robert Kiyosaki’s seminar in Almaty.\nFor free. Let’s teach you how to earn like the rich!”\n\nHall for 200 people. Charismatic presenter, translator.\nThree hours about assets, liabilities, and the thinking of the rich.\n\nAt the end: “Two-day intensive - 50,000 ₸. Today only 50% discount.\nTomorrow the price will double.”",
    "scam_training_kiyosaki_90s_opt_training_pay" to "Pay 50,000 ₸ - “investment in yourself”",
    "scam_training_kiyosaki_90s_opt_training_research" to "Look for reviews of the company in newspapers",
    "scam_training_kiyosaki_90s_opt_training_decline" to "Refuse - decisions under pressure are dangerous",
    "scam_training_business_2005_msg" to "A colleague told me about the “Money and Success” training.\n“I changed there! Charismatic coach, practice, teamwork.\nFree introductory session on Saturday. Just go.\"\n\nI came in. Three hours of energy. At the end:\n“Basic course - 80,000 ₸. Only for those who sign up today - 30% discount.\nTomorrow there will be no such price.”",
    "scam_training_business_2005_opt_training_pay" to "Pay 80,000 ₸ - “investment in yourself”",
    "scam_training_business_2005_opt_training_research" to "Google the company and reviews before paying",
    "scam_training_business_2005_opt_training_decline" to "Refuse - a decision under pressure is dangerous",
    "scam_training_bm_2015_msg" to "I saw an advertisement on Instagram: “Business Youth - Almaty.”\nFriend on WhatsApp: “I was there, it’s really fire! Go to the free webinar.\"\n\nOnline webinar - an hour of motivation, success stories.\nAt the end: “Live intensive - 80,000 ₸. Only today with a 40% discount.”\n\nI felt uplifted. But why today?",
    "scam_training_bm_2015_opt_training_pay" to "Pay 80,000 ₸ - “investment in yourself”",
    "scam_training_bm_2015_opt_training_research" to "Google the company and reviews before paying",
    "scam_training_bm_2015_opt_training_decline" to "Refuse - good things don’t come for free",
    "scam_training_cult_msg" to "Ruslan called and spent a long time trying to persuade me to go to the “Money and You” training.\n\n“I changed so much there! Charismatic speaker, powerful atmosphere. Free, just go.”\nLet's go. Three hours of energy, exercise, success stories - really exciting.\n\nAt the very end, the speaker says: “The next level is 80,000 ₸.\nBut only today with a 40% discount. Tomorrow there will be no such price.”\n\nI felt euphoric. But why does the decision need to be made right now?",
    "scam_training_cult_opt_training_pay" to "Pay 80,000 ₸ - “investment in yourself”",
    "scam_training_cult_opt_training_research" to "Google the company and reviews before paying",
    "scam_training_cult_opt_training_decline" to "Refuse - good things don’t come for free",
    "scam_training_reviews_msg" to "I found a forum with reviews. The structure is the same for all:\n— Free introductory\n— Paid basic (80k)\n— “Advanced” (200k)\n— “Master” (500k+)\n— Volunteering to organize new trainings\n\nThey don't give you real skills. NLP techniques create dependence on the group.",
    "scam_training_reviews_opt_training_research_lesson" to "Thanks to the Internet. Check first, pay later.",
    "scam_training_first_level_msg" to "3 days of intensive. Tears, hugs, “breakthroughs”.\nFeeling: “I am a different person!”\n\nIn the end: “The baseline is just the first step.\nAdvanced module - 200,000 ₸. Discount only for those who decide now.”",
    "scam_training_first_level_opt_training_escalate" to "Pay 200,000 ₸ - I feel that I need to continue",
    "scam_training_first_level_opt_training_stop" to "Stay. Emotional uplift ≠ real value.",
    "scam_training_deeper_msg" to "2 months have passed. The total costs for training are significant.\nMinimum practical skills.\n\nBut now they are asking to “help” - by volunteering at the next training.\nAnd of course - bring friends.\n\nThe organization makes money by training you to be their recruiter.",
    "scam_training_deeper_opt_training_exit" to "Exit. Quite an expensive lesson.",
    "evt_aidar_intro_2005_msg" to "2005 Almaty. Aidar is 23 years old.\n\nFive years ago, your parents borrowed money from neighbors to buy you a computer. Then it seemed like it was just an expensive toy. It turned out - a ticket to the profession.\n\nYou just got your first normal job - junior developer for 80,000 tenge per month. This is more than my father earns.\n\nOn hand - 200,000 tenge of savings. Income - 80,000 per month. Debt - 120,000 (for a laptop).\n\nA colleague just called: “Listen, there’s a topic. One company offers to invest money - 40% per month is guaranteed. I’ve already paid in, I’ll receive the first payments tomorrow.”",
    "evt_aidar_intro_2005_opt_warn_colleague" to "Warning - this is a pyramid",
    "evt_aidar_intro_2005_opt_invest" to "Invest - your colleague is not a fool",
    "evt_aidar_intro_2005_opt_focus_work" to "Focus on work. Not my topic.",
    "evt_aidar_intro_2015_msg" to "2015 Almaty. Aidar is 33 years old.\n\nYou are a lead developer in a large company. Good salary, stability. But something is itching - I’ve been in the same place for five years, ideas are accumulating.\n\nOn hand - 500,000 tenge. Income - 250,000 per month. Mortgage - 800,000 left.\n\nToday at lunch, colleagues were discussing a startup idea. One of them has already applied for the Astana Hub grant. Another has already registered an individual entrepreneur.\n\nIn the evening, an old friend wrote: “There is an offer to work at a startup. Shares instead of half the salary. I believe in the idea.\"",
    "evt_aidar_intro_2015_opt_join_startup" to "Agree - shares in an interesting project",
    "evt_aidar_intro_2015_opt_stay_safe" to "Stay. Stability is more important.",
    "evt_aidar_intro_2015_opt_own_project" to "Start your own project at night",
    "evt_aidar_intro_2024_msg" to "2024 Almaty. Aidar is 28 years old.\n\nYou are a junior developer in an outsourcing company. A year ago I moved from Shymkent. You rent an apartment with a friend and pay for a laptop.\n\nOn hand - 200,000 tenge. Income - 250,000 per month. Debt - 120,000.\n\nToday in the DevKZ Telegram channel they wrote about a hackathon with a prize of 1,000,000 tenge. Deadline is in a week.\n\nAt the same time, a colleague sent a link on WhatsApp: “Look, I invested 100k - already 140k in three days. This is crypto arbitrage.”",
    "evt_aidar_intro_2024_opt_hackathon" to "Participating in a hackathon is a real chance",
    "evt_aidar_intro_2024_opt_warn_crypto" to "Warning a colleague is a scam",
    "evt_aidar_intro_2024_opt_just_work" to "Just work. Don't spray.",
    "evt_aidar_startup_pitch_msg" to "Meeting with the startup team.\n\nIdea: a platform for online tutors in Kazakhstan. Market: 50,000 students per year. There are almost no competitors.\n\nThey offer: 15% share in exchange for six months of work at a reduced rate (minus 100,000 tenge per month from the current one).\n\nThere is a prototype. There are the first 3 clients. There is enthusiasm.",
    "evt_aidar_startup_pitch_opt_accept_equity" to "Agree - 15% can cost millions",
    "evt_aidar_startup_pitch_opt_negotiate" to "Bargain - I want 25% or full rate",
    "evt_aidar_startup_pitch_opt_decline" to "Refusing is too risky",
    "evt_aidar_startup_3months_msg" to "Three months in a startup.\n\nGood news: 47 paying customers, revenue growing.\nBad news: they burned more money than they planned. We need another 6 months.\n\nCo-founder offers two options.",
    "evt_aidar_startup_3months_opt_continue_reduced" to "Continue with a reduced rate for another 6 months",
    "evt_aidar_startup_3months_opt_find_investor" to "Find an investor - pitch funds",
    "evt_aidar_startup_3months_opt_exit" to "Leave - take the money and leave",
    "evt_aidar_startup_result_msg" to "A year has passed. Time to take stock.\n\nThe startup has reached self-sufficiency. 200+ clients. Revenue - 3,000,000 tenge per year.\n\nThe co-founder offers to sell the company to a strategic investor for 15,000,000 tenge. Your share is 15% = 2,250,000 tenge.\n\nOr continue and build further.",
    "evt_aidar_startup_result_opt_sell" to "Sell. 2.25 million is a good amount.",
    "evt_aidar_startup_result_opt_continue" to "Continue building - more potential",
    "evt_aidar_startup_success_msg" to "The deal is closed.\n\nYou received 2,250,000 tenge. The first serious money from my work.\n\nNow the question is what to do with this capital?",
    "evt_aidar_startup_success_opt_invest_etf" to "Invest in ETFs - long-term",
    "evt_aidar_startup_success_opt_new_startup" to "Launch a new startup - you have experience",
    "evt_aidar_startup_success_opt_pay_debt" to "Close all debts and create a cushion",
    "evt_aidar_senior_promotion_msg" to "You have been offered a promotion to Senior Developer.\n\nPros: +80,000 tenge to salary, more influence on architecture.\nCons: more responsibility, less time for your projects.\n\nAt the same time, an offer came from another company - 120,000 more, but you need to move to another city.",
    "evt_aidar_senior_promotion_opt_accept_internal" to "Accept an internal promotion",
    "evt_aidar_senior_promotion_opt_accept_external" to "Accept an external offer - more money",
    "evt_aidar_senior_promotion_opt_negotiate" to "Bargain—ask for more from your current employer",
    "evt_aidar_freelance_order_msg" to "A customer from Russia wrote: I need a landing page for 150,000 tenge, period - 2 weeks.\n\nThis is a good amount. But you already have a busy schedule at work.\nIf you take it, you will have to work at night for two weeks.",
    "evt_aidar_freelance_order_opt_accept" to "Take an order - you need money",
    "evt_aidar_freelance_order_opt_negotiate_deadline" to "Take it, but ask for 3 weeks",
    "evt_aidar_freelance_order_opt_decline" to "Refuse - health is more important",
    "evt_aidar_family_pressure_msg" to "Mom calls: “Son, we need money. My father got sick and needed surgery - 300,000 tenge. There is no one else to ask.\"\n\nYou now have 400,000 in savings. That's all there is.",
    "evt_aidar_family_pressure_opt_help_full" to "Give 300,000 - family is more important",
    "evt_aidar_family_pressure_opt_help_partial" to "Give 150,000 and help find the rest",
    "evt_aidar_family_pressure_opt_find_alternative" to "Help find a medical loan",
    "evt_aidar_mortgage_offer_msg" to "The bank approved a mortgage for a one-room apartment in Almaty.\n\nPrice: 18,000,000 tenge\nDown payment: 20% = 3,600,000 tenge\nMonthly payment: 180,000 tenge for 20 years\n\nRent of a similar apartment: 150,000 per month",
    "evt_aidar_mortgage_offer_opt_take_mortgage" to "Taking out a mortgage is more important than your home",
    "evt_aidar_mortgage_offer_opt_keep_renting" to "Continue to rent - mortgage is bondage",
    "evt_aidar_mortgage_offer_opt_save_more" to "Save more and take out a smaller mortgage",
    "evt_aidar_startup_aftershock_msg" to "Three months after leaving the startup.\n\nThe co-founder writes: the company was bought for 45,000,000 tenge. If you had stayed, your share would have been 6,750,000.\n\nYou received 2,250,000. The difference is 4,500,000.",
    "evt_aidar_startup_aftershock_opt_accept" to "Accept. I got good money and valuable experience.",
    "evt_aidar_startup_aftershock_opt_regret" to "It's a pity. I should have stayed.",
    "evt_aidar_normal_life_msg" to "Quiet month. Work is proceeding as usual.\n\nIn your free time, you study new technologies - you have an interest in AI and machine learning. This could open up new opportunities.\n\nWhat do you do in your free time?",
    "evt_aidar_normal_life_opt_learn_ai" to "Sign up for an AI/ML course - an investment in yourself",
    "evt_aidar_normal_life_opt_freelance" to "Taking freelance orders - additional income",
    "evt_aidar_normal_life_opt_rest" to "Rest - balance is important",
    "evt_aidar_debt_crisis_msg" to "Debts eat up almost all income.\n\nDebt: {debt}. Monthly payment: {payment}.\nAfter all the payments, there is very little left to live on.\n\nStress is growing. Something needs to change.",
    "evt_aidar_debt_crisis_opt_extra_work" to "Take a part-time job - pay off debt faster",
    "evt_aidar_debt_crisis_opt_refinance" to "Refinance at a lower interest rate",
    "evt_aidar_debt_crisis_opt_cut_expenses" to "Cut expenses to a minimum",
    "evt_aidar_burnout_warning_msg" to "You've been working nonstop for months now.\n\nStress at its limit. Headaches appeared. Sleep was disturbed.\nColleagues notice that you have become irritable.\n\nThe body signals: you need rest.",
    "evt_aidar_burnout_warning_opt_vacation" to "Take a vacation - at least a week",
    "evt_aidar_burnout_warning_opt_reduce_load" to "Reduce the load - abandon some projects",
    "evt_aidar_burnout_warning_opt_push_through" to "Just wait another month and then I’ll rest",
    "evt_aidar_investment_unlock_msg" to "Savings are growing.\n\nYou already have {capital} tenge in your savings. At this rate, you can start investing.\n\nA friend told me about index ETFs - low risk, historically 8-12% per year.",
    "evt_aidar_investment_unlock_opt_start_investing" to "Start investing - open an account",
    "evt_aidar_investment_unlock_opt_keep_saving" to "Saving cash for now - not ready for risks",
    "evt_aidar_ending_startup_king_msg" to "You've built a successful technology business.\n\nThe startup grew to 500 customers and was sold for a large sum.\nYour investments are working. There are no debts. The family is fine.\n\nThis is not luck - it is the result of making good decisions under pressure.",
    "evt_aidar_ending_startup_king_opt_celebrate" to "This is just the beginning.",
    "evt_aidar_ending_senior_dev_msg" to "You have become a respected Senior Developer.\n\nStable high salary. The apartment has been purchased. The investment portfolio is growing.\nYou chose reliability - and it bore fruit.\n\nFinancial stability has been achieved.",
    "evt_aidar_ending_senior_dev_opt_celebrate" to "A good life is deserved.",
    "evt_aidar_ending_freedom_msg" to "Financial freedom achieved.\n\nYour investments generate enough to live without having to work as needed.\nYou work because you want to - not because you have to.\n\nThis is real freedom.",
    "evt_aidar_ending_freedom_opt_enjoy" to "A new stage of life begins.",
    "evt_aidar_ending_broke_msg" to "The money has run out.\n\nA series of bad decisions - scam, debt, failed business - led to zero.\nBut the knowledge remained. And experience too.\n\nWe can start again. But already smarter.",
    "evt_aidar_ending_broke_opt_restart" to "Start again. From scratch, but with experience.",
    "evt_aidar_ending_paycheck_msg" to "Life from paycheck to paycheck.\n\nNo savings. No investment. The income is enough to live on - and no more.\nIt's not a disaster. But there was more potential.\n\nIt's not too late to change the trajectory.",
    "evt_aidar_ending_paycheck_opt_reflect" to "It's time to reconsider your priorities.",
    "evt_aidar90s_intro_msg" to "October 1993. Almaty lives in Soviet rubles, which almost no one truly respects anymore. Prices jump so quickly that people try to spend their salary on the same day: today it can be used to buy a bag of flour and meat for a wedding, in a week it may only be enough for the feast itself.\n\nAidar is twenty-two. He is still too young to consider himself broken, and already old enough to understand: if the family does not hold on now, no one will come and put it back together. Parents saved money for years, dreaming of a calm old age and a new car, and now kitchen conversations increasingly sound the same: “they saved for life, but it turned out to be a couple of good tables and one very bad year.”\n\nOn hand {capital}. Income {income}, if at all, will be paid in real money, and not in sugar or butter. Rumors are already spreading around the city that soon Kazakhstan will have its own currency and the old rubles will have to be changed in a hurry. And right now my father is calling: some people promise to return what they lost if they invest more. In the 90s, almost every hope comes to the house in a rescue suit. Aidar needs to decide whether to believe in her again.",
    "evt_aidar90s_intro_opt_warn_parents" to "Warning your father is a scam!",
    "evt_aidar90s_intro_opt_send_money_help" to "Send them your last money",
    "evt_aidar90s_intro_opt_ignore_focus_self" to "Ignore. Save yourself.",
    "evt_aidar90s_parents_conflict_msg" to "The father hangs up almost with offense. In the 90s, people defend not only money that is no longer there, but also the right to believe that it can still be returned. It’s hard for Aidar to hear distrust in his own voice, but it would be even harder to remain silent.\n\nAt work, there is also no feeling of ground under your feet. The bosses offer wages not in money, but in sugar, butter and something else that has not yet depreciated on the way home. The time is like this: everyone decides for themselves what is actually considered remuneration here.\n\nYou can take a product and turn it into an opportunity, wait for real money, or finally admit: survival requires looking for a second life outside of your main job.",
    "evt_aidar90s_parents_conflict_opt_take_goods" to "Take sugar and butter (can be sold)",
    "evt_aidar90s_parents_conflict_opt_wait_cash" to "Wait for real money",
    "evt_aidar90s_parents_conflict_opt_look_side_hustle" to "Look for part-time work in the market",
    "evt_aidar90s_parents_lost_money_msg" to "Money disappears as quickly as the people who promised to return it. Everything is repeated with frightening precision: new faces, the same words, the same funnel of shame after the door has already closed behind the scammers.\n\nThe father can't stand it. His heart gives out before he has time to say anything useful or ask for forgiveness. One day, Aidar ceases to be just a son and becomes the main breadwinner of the family, although no one asked if he was ready for such a role.\n\nNow each next choice will be harder than the previous one. Because it’s no longer about personal ambition, but about who can keep the house from completely falling apart.",
    "evt_aidar90s_parents_lost_money_opt_take_extra_job" to "Take a second shift (taxi driver)",
    "evt_aidar90s_parents_lost_money_opt_sell_computer" to "Sell ​​your PC for treatment",
    "evt_aidar90s_market_opportunity_msg" to "At a flea market, everything smells the same: dust, cheap plastic and a chance to jump out of poverty one lucky turn. Aidar is offered a shipment of Chinese watches, and the offer sounds exactly like almost all dangerous possibilities sounded in the 90s: quickly, confidently and almost believably.\n\nThere are a lot of people around who have already stopped believing in a long, honest journey. Some sell shoes, some sell cigarettes, some sell other people's promises. Against this background, risk begins to look not an exception, but the only norm of the time.\n\nTo enter, you need to invest 30,000 ₸. For some this is a small thing, for Aidar it is almost a piece of the future. But if the party succeeds, for the first time he will feel not just survival, but upward movement.",
    "evt_aidar90s_market_opportunity_opt_buy_watches" to "Put everything into a watch",
    "evt_aidar90s_market_opportunity_opt_skip_risk" to "Too dangerous. Work as a loader",
    "evt_aidar90s_no_computer_life_opt_hard_labor" to "Work in a factory",
    "evt_aidar90s_inflation_crisis_opt_cut_expenses" to "Reduce costs to a minimum",
    "evt_aidar90s_inflation_crisis_opt_borrow_money" to "Borrow from friends (at interest)",
    "evt_aidar90s_inflation_crisis_opt_find_second_job" to "Find a second job",
    "evt_aidar90s_business_opportunity_opt_decline_business" to "Refusing is too risky",
    "evt_aidar90s_business_opportunity_opt_negotiate_better" to "Bargain for a better share",
    "evt_aidar90s_kiosk_opened_opt_pay_taxes" to "Pay taxes honestly",
    "evt_aidar90s_kiosk_opened_opt_bribe_inspector" to "Give a bribe (5000 ₸)",
    "evt_aidar90s_kiosk_negotiation_opt_walk_away" to "Leave the deal",
    "evt_aidar90s_constitution_1995_opt_buy_land" to "Buy a plot of land (long-term)",
    "evt_aidar90s_constitution_1995_opt_skip_land" to "Not now - no experience",
    "evt_aidar90s_chechen_war_broadcast_opt_call_relatives_russia" to "Call your relatives in Russia and find out if everything is calm",
    "evt_aidar90s_chechen_war_broadcast_opt_listen_veteran_story" to "Linger in the courtyard and listen to the former Afghan",
    "evt_aidar90s_chechen_war_broadcast_opt_switch_off_tv" to "Turn off the TV. There are enough troubles of your own",
    "evt_aidar90s_chechen_war_veteran_story_opt_remember_peace_value" to "Remember: peace and stability are also capital",
    "evt_aidar90s_chechen_war_veteran_story_opt_go_home_after_talk" to "Return home and hold on tighter to your people",
    "evt_aidar90s_nuclear_disarmament_reaction_opt_support_disarmament" to "Think: that’s right, people already have enough of a landfill",
    "evt_aidar90s_nuclear_disarmament_reaction_opt_ask_about_semey" to "Ask elders what it looked like for families from Semey",
